{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the demo for My Party Needs An Alchemist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this light-hearted fantasy adventure game, you play as an alchemist!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a quest to save the world with a party of brave adventurers that you would come to know and love! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EXPLORE THE LEAFWOOD FOREST!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the first region of the game as you travel from quest to quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>MAKE POTIONS! USE POTIONS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/PotionMakingv3.gif?t=1729775072\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather herbs, mix them together and create wondrous Potions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use them when the time is right to fight off dangerous, magical beasts! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BECOME THE ULTIMATE SUPPORT!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/combat_3.gif?t=1729775072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Organise your party, meet new characters and help them to survive this legendary quest! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FALL IN LOVE WITH THE FIRST 4 COMPANIONS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/AdventureScene.gif?t=1729775072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help save the world in this light-hearted character-driven story!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729775072","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it